(1)
707-703 West 171st Street, west of and adjoining the N.W. corner of Fort Washington Ave. No. 703 is a 3-story frame house. November 9, 1927.
P.L. Sperr.

(2)
The same. May 23, 1929.
P.L Sperr.

(3)
The same, from another angle. 1932.
J. Clarence Davies Collection, Museum of the City of New York.
Negative No. 447.
